{"tid":43520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【結局你估唔到】螳螂捕蟬新版︰貓捉老鼠 點知隻雞撲出嚟…","createTime":"2016-12-17T14:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T15:32:39.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"416d10d3f64cddb8020853ec470e97f998ec6a58","tid":43520,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:27:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161217&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56054593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161217%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56054593&d=n8YxE2uC97LMwMDFKHBdVksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f1e9b5e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161217%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56054593&h=7078e587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161217&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56054593</a><br />\n美國芝加哥男子博爾（Daniel Boe）拍攝短片，看着他飼養的貓咪在戲弄自己的零食︰一隻老鼠。只見貓咪伸出爪子拍打老鼠，老鼠翻了個筋斗後重新站定，雙方隔着一段距離對峙着。<br />\n佔盡優勢的貓咪伺機又再進攻，小老鼠竟然也頑抗，博爾說他覺得「老鼠在打我的貓」，「老鼠站起來舉起前肢，然後攻擊和咬貓咪，牠似乎想逃開」。<br />\n博爾的貓咪亦非省油的燈，每次老鼠欲逃走都被貓咪攔下來。正當兩隻鬧得不可開交之際，令人意想不到地上演了一幕「螳螂捕蟬，黃雀在後」，一隻雞突然從旁殺出，閃電施展攻擊，不過牠的目標不是貓咪，而是一下子把老鼠叼走，俐落地殺死再吃掉，沒有犯上貓咪的錯誤。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/17/222751_13c90b5d831d52202d9f70b26a5896fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F17%2F222751_13c90b5d831d52202d9f70b26a5896fb.jpg&h=b724260b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75e7fcc71030fd39e0be8b6d02e08238f9188651","tid":43520,"uid":57646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:32:39.000Z","msg":"貓：識你老鼠咩屌你老母臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}